COUNTRY LIVING! HOME SITS IN A WOODED CLEARING WITH LOTS OF PRIVACY AND WILDLIFE. HOME IS A BI-LEVEL WITH 3 BEDROOMS AND FULL BATH ON MAIN LEVEL, FULL UNFINISHED BASEMENT, LARGE EAT IN KITCHEN. 2 CAR ATTACHED GARAGE. 10 X 10 DECK OVERLOOKING WOODS. NEEDS A LITTLE TLC WITH LOTS OF POTENTIAL! 

Agents must register as a User, enter the property address, and click on "Start Offer".
This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee).
If property was built prior to 1978, Lead Based Paint Potentially Exists.

BUYER TO VERIFY ALL MLS INFORMATION INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO SQ. FT, TAXES, FLOORING, ROOM SIZE, ROOM COUNT, UTILITIES, ETC...
